<h2 id="update-on-the-wooting-keyboard">Update on the Wooting Keyboard</h2>
<p><img src="https://i.imgur.com/ngDgHhj.jpg" alt="The Wooting Tenkeyless Keyboard" />
From the new renders I think I am slightly more interested in this keyboard. The new design is much simpler and does inspire hope for this keybords future. As yet this keyboards key feature has not been revealed, but it is certainly worth watching. <a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/MechanicalKeyboards/comments/3okn08/photos_we_revised_the_wooting_keyboard_design_w/cvy2dh0">The key feature or features are going to be revealed soon.</a></p>

