<h2 id="thkb-update">THKB Update</h2>
<p><img src="https://i.imgur.com/cZcGrJ7.jpg" alt="Tiny hacking keyboard" />
ne0phyte is back working on the THKB which is a 40% (39 key) HHKB esque keyboard. Another prototype has been assembled and things are looking good. For those interested you may still be able to get a prototype PCB. But it seems this has been quite popular. But I wouldnâ€™t worry if you really want one. This is great groupbuy material and I imagine it could be quite successful. This is a custom keyboard with Atmega32u4 so it will have no problem running TMK giving you a completely customisable keyboard.</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://deskthority.net/workshop-f7/thkb-tiny-hacking-keyboard-40-t6455-120.html#p258593">Prototype PCBâ€™s Here</a></li>
</ul>

